gov.nih.nlm.swing
Class Version

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.swing.Version
public class Version
extends Object

The Version class aggregates change information for the gov.nih.nlm.swing package. Eventually, it may be used to maintain its own version information. History:

06/17/2005
Some work on javadoc comments and standardizing formatting.
12/27/2004
Version tracking class was created.

Author:
MEME Group
